<!-- Definition and medical uses -->
'''避孕隔膜'''（diaphragm）是一種屏障式的[[生育控制|生育控制]]方法<ref name=Hil2008>{{cite book|last1=Hillard|first1=Paula J. Adams|last2=Hillard|first2=Paula Adams|title=The 5-minute Obstetrics and Gynecology Consult|date=2008|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|isbn=9780781769426|page=240|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=fOoFIQOdIhkC&lpg=PA240|language=en}}</ref>。正常使用下，一年內的失敗率為12%，屬於成功率中等的避孕方式<ref>{{cite book|last1=Wipf|first1=Joyce|title=Women's Health, An Issue of Medical Clinics of North America,|date=2015|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|isbn=9780323376082|page=508|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=fJzuCQAAQBAJ&pg=PA508|language=en}}</ref>。使用方式是配合[[殺精劑|殺精劑]]使用，在性行為放在[[子宮頸|子宮頸]]前，且在性行為至少六個小時後才能取出<ref name=CDC2016/><ref name=Helm2006>{{cite book|last1=Helms|first1=Richard A.|last2=Quan|first2=David J.|title=Textbook of Therapeutics: Drug and Disease Management|date=2006|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|isbn=9780781757348|page=419|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=aVmRWrknaWgC&lpg=PA429|language=en}}</ref>。一般會需要醫療人員協助確認是否適合<ref name=CDC2016>{{cite web|title=Contraception {{!}} Reproductive Health {{!}} CDC|url=https://www.cdc.gov/reproductivehealth/contraception/|website=www.cdc.gov|accessdate=1 January 2017|date=21 June 2016}}</ref>。

<!-- Side effects and mechanism -->
避孕隔膜的副作用很少<ref name=Helm2006/>，可能會增加[[細菌性陰道炎|細菌性陰道炎]]及[[泌尿道感染|泌尿道感染]]的風險<ref name=Hil2008/>。若置於[[阴道|阴道]]未取出超過24小時，可能會造成[[中毒性休克症候群|中毒性休克症候群]] <ref name=Helm2006/>。避孕隔膜可能可以減少[[性傳染疾病|性傳染疾病]]的風險，不過無法完全阻隔性傳染疾病<ref name=Hil2008/>。有許多不同種類的避孕隔膜，差異在外環及彈性結構設計的不同<!-- <ref name=Cor1995/> -->。避孕隔膜的材質有[[乳膠|乳膠]]、[[矽膠|矽膠]]及[[天然橡膠|天然橡膠]] <!-- <ref name=Cor1995/> -->。其工作原理是不讓精子進入子宮頸，而且讓配合使用的殺精劑發揮作用<ref name=Cor1995>{{cite book|last1=Corson|first1=S. L.|last2=Derman|first2=R. J.|title=Fertility Control|date=1995|publisher=CRC Press|isbn=9780969797807|pages=211-212|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=30EzZPp1ypYC&lpg=PA213&dq=Diaphragm%20latex%20silicone&pg=PA211|language=en}}</ref>。

<!-- History, society and culture -->
避孕隔膜是在1882年問世的<ref name=Su2014>{{cite book|last1=Everett|first1=Suzanne|title=Handbook of Contraception and Sexual Health|date=2014|publisher=Routledge|isbn=9781135114114|page=62|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=8j9FAwAAQBAJ&lpg=PA61&dq=Diaphragm%20contraception%20history&pg=PA62|language=en}}</ref>。是[[世界衛生組織基礎藥物|世界衛生組織基礎藥物]]之一，是醫療系統需要的基礎藥物<ref name=WHO19th>{{cite web|title=WHO Model List of Essential Medicines (19th List)|url=http://www.who.int/medicines/publications/essentialmedicines/EML_2015_FINAL_amended_NOV2015.pdf?ua=1|work=World Health Organization|accessdate=8 December 2016|date=April 2015}}</ref>。在英國[[國民保健署_(英國)|國民保健署]]為每個避孕隔膜的費用少於10英鎊<ref name=BNF69>{{cite book|title=British national formulary : BNF 69|url=https://archive.org/details/bnf69britishnati0000unse|date=2015|publisher=British Medical Association|isbn=9780857111562|page=[https://archive.org/details/bnf69britishnati0000unse/page/559 559]|edition=69}}</ref>。在美國價格約15至75美元，有0.3%的人用避孕隔膜進行避孕<ref name=Sh2011>{{cite book|last1=Shoupe|first1=Donna|title=Contraception|date=2011|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=9781444342635|page=15|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=ksjJcx1CeKcC&lpg=PA15&dq=Diaphragm%20contraception%20cost%20united%20states&pg=PA15|language=en}}</ref>。上述的費用不含殺精劑<ref>{{cite book|last1=Alexander|first1=Linda|last2=LaRosa|first2=Judith|title=New Dimensions In Women's Health|date=2009|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|isbn=9780763765927|page=94|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=2X03PXd4JSoC&lpg=PA94&dq=Diaphragm%20contraception%20millions&pg=PA94|language=en}}</ref>。

